metadata.name: 2476 Attention Token (Moving to Polygon) Souvenir only on eth
metadata.description:
2476 Attention Token is a token that can be staked for the attention of 2476 - this attention is not guaranteed, and the token has no value on it's own, no purchase is necessary for 2476's attention. 

Important Update!!! the 2476 token is moving to Polygon soon due to high gas fees on eth, the Polygon token will be airdropped to all holders
